Item List Management Application

The Item List Management Application is a web-based tool that allows users to manage a list of items efficiently. The application provides the following key functionalities:

Add an Element: Users can easily add new items to the list. The application provides a user-friendly interface where users can enter the details of the item, such as its name, description, quantity, and any other relevant information. Upon submission, the item is added to the list and becomes immediately available for further management.

Delete an Item: Users can remove items from the list as needed. By selecting an item from the list and initiating the delete action, the application promptly removes the selected item from the list. This functionality ensures that users can maintain an up-to-date and organized item list, removing any items that are no longer relevant or needed.

Search Item: The application offers a search feature that enables users to quickly locate specific items within the list. Users can enter search criteria, such as the item name or a keyword, and the application will filter the list to display only the items that match the search query. This search functionality helps users find items efficiently, even when the list grows larger over time.

The Item List Management Application aims to provide a streamlined and user-friendly experience for managing a list of items. It leverages modern web technologies to ensure optimal performance and responsiveness. The application's intuitive interface, along with the convenient add, delete, and search functionalities, empowers users to efficiently organize and retrieve information about their items.
